snippet.title: TimeTravelAstronaut
snippet.description:
I enjoy swearing at videogames, while I happen to be recording it. Usually 2 game series run concurrently, with daily uploads. You can request a game to be played, but there's several in the queue since they're usually rather long games. 

I stream here on Youtube every Sunday/Wednesday/Friday.

You can come visit my forum if you want to discuss random junk with myself or others: http://ttastro.proboards.com/

If you enjoy my stuff and are interested in supporting my videos, take a gander at my patron: https://www.patreon.com/tta
